short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A feature-rich Chrome Extension for PDF Management

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Experience the full potential of your PDFs with our cutting-edge PDF Management Extension for Chrome! Unlock a suite of powerful features, including seamless file conversion, merging, and compression, all designed to streamline your document workflow.

Effortlessly transform PDF documents into editable Word files and vice versa, 
Combine numerous files into one cohesive PDF format using our intuitive merge function and
compress PDF files without sacrificing quality.
